Fused Well-Being				KEY:Plague Eater ~ Fused Well-Being							CATEGORY:Spiritualist Class Feature				TYPE:Spiritualist Class Feature.SpecialQuality.Supernatural				SOURCEPAGE:p.12														DESC:At 10th level, a plague eater always gains the benefits of bonded senses when her phantom is manifested. She also gains the skill ranks and bonus to resist disease granted by the spirit’s emotional focus, even when her phantom is manifested.		DESC:This replaces fused consciousness.|!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Archetype,Spiritualist Archetype ~ Plague Eater
